### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@email = admin@empresa-demo.com
@password = admin123

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 3. Register (nuevo usuario)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nuevo@empresa-demo.com",
  "name": "Nuevo Usuario",
  "password": "password123",
  "companyName": "Nueva Empresa"
}

### 4. Obtener empresa (requiere token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/companies
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Crear proyecto
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Proyecto de Prueba"
}

### 6. Obtener proyectos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Crear producto
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto de Prueba",
  "sku": "PROD-001",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}"
}

### 8. Obtener productos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Obtener productos por proyecto
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?projectId={{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Actualizar producto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto Actualizado",
  "sku": "PROD-001-UPDATED"
}

### 11. Obtener producto espec√≠fico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Eliminar producto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Eliminar proyecto
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



